{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure protected wellbeing days for employees in addition to annual & sick leave",
        "additional_details": "Employees can call in sick when physically or mentally unwell, but there is no equivalent option for people experiencing exceptionally positive wellbeing. We ask the Government to introduce limited protected \u201cwellbeing days\u201d or \u201ccall well\u201d leave, allowing employees to take occasional time off to maintain positive mental health, prevent burnout, and support long-term wellbeing and work-life balance.",
        "background": "We want the Government to introduce a legal right for employees to take occasional wellbeing days, in addition to sick leave and annual leave, to support positive mental health, prevent burnout, and improve work-life balance.",
